:: the following command is used to give timeout in the code

:: This is a timeout of 10 Seconds after which it will quit proceed to the next command
timeout /t 10 

:: assignment of a value to a variable is done like this

set "Variable=Value"

echo %Variable% ::This is how you use a variable

